## Exact diff — Matrix frontproxy (versioned, PR #55)

The `client_max_body_size 100m;` override for `matrix.hl.maier.wtf` is now a
managed vhost file (`pi/compose/vhost.d/matrix.hl.maier.wtf_location`) mounted
into the frontproxy at `/etc/nginx/vhost.d`, so a host rebuild from this repo
reproduces the working state (fixes Element web-app upload that returned
HTTP 413).

